Ali ABDI and Emaniam Abdi, Plaintiffs,
v.
Joseph LOONAM and Danielle Loonam, Defendants. Joseph Loonam and Danielle Loonam, Plaintiffs-Respondents,
v.
Ali Abdi and Emanian Abdi a/k/a Effat S. Emaniam, Defendants-Petitioners. C-14 September Term 2018
080714 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000397-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
